    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are no chips, dents, or scratches to be found anywhere. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, smelling fresh and showing zero wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been meticulously garaged and maintained with no expense spared, making this an exceptional find for a discerning buyer who demands the very best.",
