    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? This car is in fair condition and has plenty of life left in it! While it shows some honest wear from its time on the road, it remains a dependable choice for anyone seeking a solid, functional vehicle at a great value. It's a fantastic opportunity to own a capable car that\u2019s ready to get you where you need to go!",
