    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she's been an absolute gem. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and drives like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the brand-new price tag! I've taken great care of it, and it's ready to hit the road for many more adventures. If you're looking for a smooth, comfy drive that's been well-loved, you've found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great home!",
