    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a desirable 6-speed manual transmission. This example is mechanically sound, with the critical VANOS system recently serviced and a preventative subframe reinforcement kit already installed. The engine pulls hard to its 8,000 RPM redline, breathing through factory individual throttle bodies. Handling remains sharp thanks to a refreshed suspension featuring poly-bushings and an M Variable Differential Lock that ensures precise torque distribution. While the exterior shows minor cosmetic wear consistent with an honest 'good' condition enthusiast car, the drivetrain and chassis geometry are dialed in for peak performance.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 32
    },
    {
